---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const tokenUrl = "https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new?name=Academic%20Homepage%20Editor&description=Edit%20sci-m-wang.github.io%20content&target_name=sci-m-wang&expires_in=90&contents=write";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Edit homepage · Ming Wang"
  description="Private, browser-based content editor for Ming Wang's academic homepage."
  noindex={true}
  secureEditor={true}
>
  <main class="update-page portal-page" id="main">
    <nav class="update-page__nav" aria-label="Homepage editor navigation">
      <a href="/">← Ming Wang / 王明</a>
      <span>OWNER EDITOR · DIRECT PUBLISH</span>
    </nav>

    <section class="update-page__hero portal-hero">
      <p class="section-heading__index">Private content desk / 私人内容工作台</p>
      <div>
        <h1>Edit here.<br />Publish once.</h1>
        <p>Review existing records, add new work, and publish directly from this page. No GitHub Actions forms are required.</p>
        <p>在本页直接查看、添加与修改内容，确认后即可发布，不再需要操作 GitHub Actions 表单。</p>

        <aside class="security-note" aria-label="Security model">
          <span class="security-note__mark">✓</span>
          <div>
            <h2>GitHub remains the authorization authority.</h2>
            <p>The editor accepts only the repository owner's fine-grained token with write access to this repository. The token stays in page memory, is sent only to GitHub's API, and disappears when the page is refreshed or closed.</p>
            <p>编辑器只接受仓库所有者、且仅对本仓库有写权限的细粒度 Token。Token 仅保存在当前页面内存中，只发送给 GitHub API，刷新或关闭页面即清除。</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="portal-alert" id="portal-alert" role="status" aria-live="polite" hidden></div>

    <section class="portal-auth" id="auth-panel" aria-labelledby="auth-title">
      <div class="portal-auth__intro">
        <p class="section-heading__index">01 · Verify ownership / 验证身份</p>
        <h2 id="auth-title">Connect your GitHub account.</h2>
        <p>Use a fine-grained token restricted to <strong>sci-m-wang/sci-m-wang.github.io</strong> with only <strong>Contents: Read and write</strong>.</p>
        <p>使用仅限该仓库、且只有 <strong>Contents: Read and write</strong> 权限的细粒度 Token。</p>
      </div>

      <form class="portal-auth__form" id="auth-form" autocomplete="off">
        <label class="portal-field portal-field--wide" for="github-token">
          <span>Fine-grained token <small>不会被保存</small></span>
          <input
            id="github-token"
            name="github-token"
            type="password"
            placeholder="github_pat_…"
            autocomplete="off"
            autocapitalize="none"
            spellcheck="false"
            required
          />
        </label>
        <div class="portal-auth__actions">
          <button class="portal-action portal-action--primary" id="connect-button" type="submit">连接并打开编辑器</button>
          <a class="portal-action portal-action--line" href={tokenUrl} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">创建专用 Token ↗</a>
        </div>
        <details class="portal-token-guide">
          <summary>第一次使用？查看 4 步设置</summary>
          <ol>
            <li>打开“创建专用 Token”，Resource owner 选择 <strong>sci-m-wang</strong>。</li>
            <li>Repository access 选择 <strong>Only select repositories</strong>，仅勾选 <strong>sci-m-wang.github.io</strong>。</li>
            <li>Repository permissions 中仅将 <strong>Contents</strong> 设为 <strong>Read and write</strong>。</li>
            <li>生成后复制 Token，回到本页粘贴。建议设置 90 天有效期，到期后重新生成。</li>
          </ol>
        </details>
      </form>
    </section>

    <section class="portal-editor" id="editor-panel" aria-labelledby="editor-title" hidden>
      <header class="portal-account-bar">
        <div class="portal-account" id="portal-account">
          <span class="portal-account__avatar" aria-hidden="true">MW</span>
          <span><strong id="account-name">sci-m-wang</strong><small>Verified repository owner</small></span>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-account-bar__actions">
          <a href="https://github.com/sci-m-wang/sci-m-wang.github.io/commits/master" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">提交记录 ↗</a>
          <button id="logout-button" type="button">退出编辑</button>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="portal-editor__heading">
        <div>
          <p class="section-heading__index">02 · Edit & publish / 编辑并发布</p>
          <h2 id="editor-title">Content archive</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Every save creates one traceable Git commit and automatically rebuilds the homepage.<br />每次保存都会生成一条可追踪的 Git 提交，并自动更新主页。</p>
      </div>

      <nav class="portal-tabs" aria-label="Content type">
        <button class="portal-tab is-active" type="button" data-section="publications"><span>01</span>论文 Publications</button>
        <button class="portal-tab" type="button" data-section="funding"><span>02</span>Funding</button>
        <button class="portal-tab" type="button" data-section="news"><span>03</span>动态 News</button>
        <button class="portal-tab" type="button" data-section="profile"><span>04</span>主页信息 Profile</button>
      </nav>

      <div class="portal-workspace">
        <aside class="portal-library" aria-label="Existing entries">
          <div class="portal-library__toolbar">
            <label for="entry-search">搜索条目</label>
            <input id="entry-search" type="search" placeholder="输入标题或年份" />
          </div>
          <button class="portal-new-button" id="new-entry-button" type="button">＋ 新增论文</button>
          <div class="portal-entry-list" id="entry-list" role="list"></div>
        </aside>

        <section class="portal-form-surface" aria-label="Entry editor">
          <div class="portal-empty-state" id="empty-state">
            <span>←</span>
            <h3>Choose an entry to edit.</h3>
            <p>从左侧选择已有条目，或点击“新增”开始录入。</p>
          </div>

          <form class="portal-content-form" id="content-form" novalidate hidden>
            <header class="portal-content-form__header">
              <div>
                <p class="section-heading__index" id="form-mode">Editing existing entry</p>
                <h3 id="form-title">Publication</h3>
              </div>
              <button class="portal-text-button" id="cancel-edit-button" type="button">取消</button>
            </header>

            <div class="portal-fields" id="form-fields"></div>

            <label class="portal-field portal-field--wide" for="commit-message">
              <span>提交说明 <small>Commit message</small></span>
              <input id="commit-message" type="text" maxlength="120" required />
            </label>

            <aside class="portal-save-note">
              <strong>Save path / 保存路径</strong>
              <span id="save-path">src/data/publications.json → master</span>
              <p>保存前会再次检查远端版本；如有更新冲突，本页不会覆盖新数据。</p>
            </aside>

            <footer class="portal-content-form__footer">
              <p id="form-feedback" aria-live="polite">检查必填项后即可发布。</p>
              <button class="portal-action portal-action--primary" id="save-button" type="submit">保存并发布</button>
            </footer>
          </form>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="portal-footnote">
      <p class="section-heading__index">Security notes / 安全说明</p>
      <div>
        <p>Public visitors can see this page but cannot read private credentials or publish changes. GitHub verifies the token, owner identity, repository permission, file version, and commit on every save.</p>
        <p>普通访客可以看到入口页面，但无法取得凭据或发布修改。每次保存均由 GitHub 核验 Token、所有者身份、仓库权限、文件版本与提交记录。</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script src="../scripts/update-portal.js"></script>
</BaseLayout>
